sections.heading: License; person on national registry
sections.text: The department may issue a license to any individual who has a current certificate from the National Registry of Emergency Medical Technicians.SourceLaws 1997, LB 138, ยง 18;R.S.1943, (2003), ยง 71-5189;Laws 2007, LB463, ยง 513;Laws 2018, LB1034, ยง 27.
